P(X=a) = \lim_{T \to \infty} \int_{\mathbb{R}} \frac{\sin T(x-a)}{T(x-a)}dP_X(x)
\left|\frac{\sin(T \cdot (x-a))}{T \cdot (x-a)}\right| \leq \frac{1}{T \cdot (x-a)} \to 0 \qquad (T \to \infty)
